data.eml:eml: Systematics and distribution of the giant fossil barn owls of the West Indies (Aves: Strigiformes: Tytonidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Suárez, William, Olson, Storrs L. (2015): Systematics and distribution of the giant fossil barn owls of the West Indies (Aves: Strigiformes: Tytonidae). Zootaxa 4020 (3): 533-553, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4020.3.7
